<para style="q1">

<verse number="32" style="v" />They also angered Yahweh at the waters of Meribah,</para>

<para style="q1">and Moses suffered because of them.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="33" style="v" />They made Moses bitter,</para>

<para style="q1">and he spoke rashly.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="34" style="v" />They did not destroy the nations</para>

<para style="q1">as Yahweh had commanded them,</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="35" style="v" />but they mingled with the nations</para>

<para style="q1">and learned their ways</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="36" style="v" />and worshiped their idols,</para>

<para style="q1">which became a snare to them.</para>
